From e7ab5fbb26dd4a8c7f8b885fd55b8891456e6e05 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 17:58:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix all unchecked E2E issues from issue #196 across
 Associations, Communications, and Accounting modules
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Associations:
- Add Users card to PLATFORM_ADMIN dashboard; add Maintenance card to TENANT_ADMIN dashboard
- Fix mobile sidebar: Maintenance link was missing role guard (showed to PLATFORM_ADMIN)
- Fix sidebar Users link for PLATFORM_ADMIN pointing to wrong route (/settings → /users)
- Create UserManagementPage with invite, activate/deactivate, delete; add /dashboard/users route
- Fix association form: validation message and API error extraction both used wrong field
- Fix unit create: error toast showed error code ("UNIT_ERROR") instead of readable message
- Fix renter info in unit edit: both edit pages read unit.renter?.firstName (undefined) instead of unit.renterFirstName; renter fields were also missing from the update payload

Communications:
- Implement AccountingVariableResolver: resolve {{balance}} and {{amount}} from unit balance per owner; {{dueDate}} and {{invoiceNumber}} return empty string until invoice data is available
- Fix RescheduleEmailModal: remove subject/body/recipients/template fields that were shown but never saved — modal now shows only date and time
- Fix SmsServiceImpl.toResponse: hardcoded "Recipients" replaced with message.getRecipientLabel()

Accounting:
- Add bulk delete (multi-select checkboxes) to Chart of Accounts and Banking tab
- New backend endpoints: DELETE /api/v1/accounting/coa/bulk and DELETE /api/v1/accounting/banking/bulk
- Issue #11 (confirm account number on edit) was already fixed in AddBankingPage.jsx via !isEdit guard

